  "instructions": [
    "Wash all vegetables thoroughly and pat dry.",
    "Dice carrot, celery, onion, cucumber, and tomato into bite-sized cubes.",
    "Roughly tear tarragon leaves and add them to the diced vegetables.",
    "In a small bowl whisk together olive oil, lemon juice, salt, pepper, cumin, and paprika to make the vinaigrette.",
    "Pour the dressing over the salad and toss gently until all ingredients are coated.",
    "Fold in crumbled feta cheese just before serving.",
    "Plate the salad on chilled plates and serve immediately."
